highlights.text: “Starboy” by The Weeknd and Daft Punk has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 3 weeks straight.
“Photograph” by Ed Sheeran is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 62 spots at #41.
“Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #1.
The Weeknd has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Starboy” is the highest at #3.
